Hyperiums Alliance Tool is a tool used to plan / synchronize attacks, defenses, and others alliance related things.
It will also contain some other tools to calculate fleets, etc...

It uses :

- Mangstadt PHP-HAPI ( https://github.com/mangstadt/PHP-HAPI ) to query Hyperiums.
- Cloudhead LessCSS  ( https://github.com/cloudhead/less.js ) for the CSS.
- Images from hyperiums.com